snippet.title: Breaking: PM Modi Reaches To Meet President Pranab Mukherjee

localized.description:
PM Modi has reached the Rashtrapati Bhavan to meet Pranab Mukherjee to give him updates on the actions he has taken to deal after the army base in Uri was attacked and 18 soldiers were killed.
